data.description: Experience the enchantment of serene country living in this meticulously renovated four-bedroom home. Every detail has been thoughtfully crafted, from the fully remodeled kitchen with brand-new stainless-steel appliances, custom-built island, and hickory cabinets to the dining room, living room, bedrooms, and bathrooms.  Nestled within tranquil surroundings, this residence offers a spacious layout with a versatile bonus room perfect for a 5th bedroom or office. Enjoy the convenience of a large full bath, convenient half bath, first-floor laundry, and central air.  Step outside onto the expansive back deck and be greeted by picturesque views of the West Canada Creek, creating a retreat for relaxation and enjoyment.  Embrace the tranquility of country living at its finest, yet close to Utica, Herkimer and all amenities.  Schedule your showing today!
